text: Dorcus tenuihirsutus is a beetle species of the family Lucanidae described from Korea in 2010 by Sang Il Kim and Jin-Ill Kim. ==References== * ; 2010: Review of family Lucanidae (Insecta: Coleoptera) in Korea with the description of one new species. title: Dorcus tenuihirsutus
